374
00:26:45,224 --> 00:26:48,291
<font color="yellow">Did you go to Mi-poong's dumpling store again?</font>

375
00:26:49,013 --> 00:26:52,080
<font color="yellow">That family has nothing to do with us anymore!</font>

376
00:26:52,459 --> 00:26:57,411
<font color="yellow">Whatever. I'm going with my own
two feet, so mind your own business.</font>

377
00:26:58,162 --> 00:27:03,710
<font color="yellow">Mother, that dumpling store
