378
00:27:03,904 --> 00:27:05,339
<font color="yellow">Doesn't that anger you?</font>

379
00:27:05,792 --> 00:27:10,119
<font color="yellow">If you live such a hardscrabble life,
all of your blessings will disappear!</font>

380
00:27:10,345 --> 00:27:13,416
<font color="yellow">Jang-go bought that store
for them because they deserved it!</font>

381
00:27:13,873 --> 00:27:16,748
<font color="yellow">Thanks to Jang-go, Mi-poong's
family was able to meet</font>

382
00:27:16,773 --> 00:27:19,541
<font color="yellow">her father whom they
thought was dead all this time.</font>

383
00:27:19,982 --> 00:27:23,151
<font color="yellow">Jang-go will become very blessed!</font>

384
00:27:23,865 --> 00:27:25,855
<font color="yellow">What did you say? They were able to meet</font>

385
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:28,002
<font color="yellow">her father whom they
thought was dead all this time?</font>

386
00:27:28,732 --> 00:27:30,907
<font color="yellow">Why are you so shocked?</font>

387
00:27:31,594 --> 00:27:34,024
<font color="yellow">It's my granddaughter-in-law
who found her father.</font>

388
00:27:34,490 --> 00:27:36,544
<font color="yellow">Mother, what are you talking about?</font>

389
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:38,544
<font color="yellow">What do you mean she met her father?</font>

390
00:27:38,995 --> 00:27:41,989
<font color="yellow">She thought her father had died while
they were escapingNorth Korea,</font>

391
00:27:42,388 --> 00:27:45,099
<font color="yellow">but he came to the dumpling store,</font>

392
00:27:45,287 --> 00:27:47,161
<font color="yellow">although they did lose him.</font>

393
00:27:47,787 --> 00:27:49,768
<font color="yellow">Why would they lose him when they met?</font>

394
00:27:49,993 --> 00:27:53,809
<font color="yellow">It seems like he lost his memory.
He didn't recognize them and just ran off.</font>

395
00:27:54,271 --> 00:27:59,204
<font color="yellow">So Mi-poong and her mother are
going crazy trying to find him.</font>

396
00:28:00,201 --> 00:28:03,116
<font color="yellow">- They said they were going
to buy dumplings today.
- What's wrong?</font>

