00:28:03,141 --> 00:28:05,872
<font color="yellow">- Chung-ja! What's wrong?
- What's wrong? Are you okay?</font>

398
00:28:06,670 --> 00:28:08,355
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you all of a sudden?</font>

399
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:11,455
<font color="yellow">I'm okay. I just have anemia lately.</font>

400
00:28:12,247 --> 00:28:14,729
<font color="yellow">I'll be leaving now. Bye, Geum-sil.</font>

401
00:28:14,754 --> 00:28:18,655
<font color="yellow">- Chung-ja, don't forget my favor!
