402
00:28:22,232 --> 00:28:24,317
<font color="yellow">She must be eating
all the best things in life.</font>

403
00:28:24,551 --> 00:28:28,145
<font color="yellow">Why would she have anemia? Why would
she faint all the time? My goodness.</font>

404
00:28:28,638 --> 00:28:29,638
<font color="yellow">That's odd.</font>

405
00:28:31,091 --> 00:28:32,091
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae!</font>

406
00:28:32,795 --> 00:28:35,762
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae, we're in big trouble!
