409
00:28:45,349 --> 00:28:46,733
<font color="yellow">It's Mi-poong's dumpling store!</font>

410
00:28:47,576 --> 00:28:50,796
<font color="yellow">What? What are you talking about?</font>

411
00:28:51,169 --> 00:28:53,672
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong opened up a dumpling store.</font>

412
00:28:53,899 --> 00:28:56,515
<font color="yellow">Her dad came by the store
yesterday, but she lost him,</font>

413
00:28:56,540 --> 00:28:59,272
<font color="yellow">so she's going crazy looking for him!</font>

414
00:29:00,795 --> 00:29:02,778
<font color="yellow">Impossible.</font>

415
00:29:03,521 --> 00:29:07,601
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim and his son wouldn't have
met Mi-poong already, would they?</font>

416
00:29:08,130 --> 00:29:09,130
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

417
00:29:09,630 --> 00:29:13,497
<font color="yellow">He was at the company.
His meeting ended just now.</font>

418
00:29:16,951 --> 00:29:18,333
<font color="yellow">Is Mr. Kim in his office?</font>

419
00:29:19,795 --> 00:29:20,928
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

420
00:29:21,521 --> 00:29:22,521
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

421
00:29:23,412 --> 00:29:26,075
<font color="yellow">What did he say?
He's not in his office, is he?</font>

422
00:29:26,442 --> 00:29:30,560
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness. They must have
gone already. What do we do now?</font>

423
00:29:31,130 --> 00:29:34,153
<font color="yellow">Do you know where that dumpling
store is? Hurry up and find out.</font>

424
00:29:34,178 --> 00:29:36,626
<font color="yellow">Okay, I can find out. Hold on.</font>

425
00:29:40,185 --> 00:29:43,188
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil, where is that
dumpling store located?</font>

426
00:29:49,826 --> 00:29:51,982
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness! It's true!</font>

427
00:29:52,677 --> 00:29:55,142
<font color="yellow">They even named it Father's Dumplings!</font>

428
00:29:55,167 --> 00:29:59,552
<font color="yellow">- (Father's Dumplings)
- Oh my god. Shin-ae,
what can we do about them?</font>

429
00:30:00,810 --> 00:30:04,005
<font color="yellow">I just want to set that store on fire!</font>

430
00:30:04,748 --> 00:30:08,335
<font color="yellow">We told them to America, but
they wouldn't! Why are they doing this?</font>

431
00:30:08,888 --> 00:30:11,325
<font color="yellow">He must have gone there by
coincidence while at night.</font>

432
00:30:11,912 --> 00:30:13,739
<font color="yellow">He won't be able to find this dumpling store.</font>

433
00:30:14,388 --> 00:30:16,766
<font color="yellow">Yes. He doesn't even know the Seoul streets-</font>

434
00:30:18,388 --> 00:30:19,388
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

435
00:30:19,904 --> 00:30:22,669
<font color="yellow">He's coming with Mr. Kim over there!</font>

436
00:30:32,693 --> 00:30:33,693
<font color="yellow">Come out.</font>

437
00:30:37,646 --> 00:30:39,646
<font color="yellow">I think it was somewhere here.</font>

438
00:30:40,295 --> 00:30:44,115
<font color="yellow">How did they come here? What do we do?</font>

439
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:47,607
<font color="yellow">Mother, stay still. Stay still!</font>

440
00:30:48,498 --> 00:30:50,945
<font color="yellow">Do you think this is the wrong place, too?</font>

441
00:30:51,357 --> 00:30:56,569
<font color="yellow">This place seems right...
but it seems wrong, too...</font>

442
00:30:57,589 --> 00:31:01,291
<font color="yellow">Father, all Seoul streets look the same.</font>

443
00:31:01,504 --> 00:31:02,737
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

444
00:31:03,307 --> 00:31:06,249
<font color="yellow">How would you be able to memorize
a street that you only came once?</font>

445
00:31:06,274 --> 00:31:12,266
<font color="yellow">But Dae-hoon, do you remember
the name of the dumpling store?</font>

446
00:31:12,590 --> 00:31:16,016
<font color="yellow">I was so hungry back then. I only looked at</font>

447
00:31:16,041 --> 00:31:19,466
<font color="yellow">- the dumplings. I didn't see the sign.
- I see.</font>

448
00:31:19,918 --> 00:31:21,803
<font color="yellow">Let's take our time searching for it.</font>

449
00:31:22,300 --> 00:31:26,125
<font color="yellow">Since we're here, let's go
to that alley over there.</font>

450
00:31:26,707 --> 00:31:28,573
<font color="yellow">- Over there.
- Yes, father.</font>

451
00:31:40,675 --> 00:31:42,191
<font color="yellow">Hold on. I'm getting a call.</font>

452
00:31:46,816 --> 00:31:48,605
<font color="yellow">Oh, it's Shin-ae.</font>

453
00:31:51,066 --> 00:31:52,066
<font color="yellow">Hi, Shin-ae.</font>

454
00:31:52,636 --> 00:31:55,511
<font color="yellow">Grandfather, where are you? I'm sick!</font>

455
00:31:58,410 --> 00:32:02,912
<font color="yellow">Okay! Your father and
I will be home immediately!</font>

456
00:32:03,308 --> 00:32:04,566
<font color="yellow">Okay. Bye.</font>

457
00:32:05,215 --> 00:32:06,542
<font color="yellow">Father, what's wrong?</font>

458
00:32:06,567 --> 00:32:09,361
<font color="yellow">- Shin-ae seems to be very sick.
- Huh?</font>

459
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:11,267
<font color="yellow">Let's hurry up and go.</font>

460
00:32:12,863 --> 00:32:15,341
<font color="yellow">Where is she sick? Hurry up and get in.</font>

461
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:31,170
<font color="yellow">Good job. You did well.</font>

462
00:32:32,277 --> 00:32:33,659
<font color="yellow">Thank goodness.</font>

463
00:32:34,418 --> 00:32:37,350
<font color="yellow">Like you said, it seems like he doesn't
know where the dumpling store is.</font>

464
00:32:37,785 --> 00:32:40,909
<font color="yellow">We need to arrive at home
before grandfather does.</font>

465
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:44,667
<font color="yellow">- Hurry up and go! Hurry!
- Okay.</font>

466
00:32:48,886 --> 00:32:53,597
<font color="yellow">You were completely fine
when I saw you at the company earlier.</font>

467
00:32:54,668 --> 00:32:56,261
<font color="yellow">What happened?</font>

468
00:32:56,472 --> 00:32:59,261
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae had acute indigestion.</font>

469
00:33:00,011 --> 00:33:06,399
<font color="yellow">She must have been very shocked
about not knowing her dad's whereabouts.</font>

470
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:08,000
<font color="yellow">Of course she must have been.</font>

471
00:33:08,730 --> 00:33:12,240
<font color="yellow">But Shin-ae, you don't have to worry anymore.</font>

472
00:33:12,847 --> 00:33:17,714
<font color="yellow">Your father returned safely, and
something like this will never happen again.</font>

473
00:33:18,418 --> 00:33:20,643
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae, don't worry.</font>

474
00:33:21,863 --> 00:33:22,863
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

475
00:33:24,027 --> 00:33:25,027
<font color="yellow">Okay, dad.</font>

476
00:33:26,418 --> 00:33:28,980
<font color="yellow">But you said you were going to buy dumplings.</font>

477
00:33:29,768 --> 00:33:32,630
<font color="yellow">- Did you find the dumpling store?
