478
00:33:33,425 --> 00:33:39,044
<font color="yellow">Dae-hoon doesn't remember where it is at all.</font>

479
00:33:40,535 --> 00:33:45,886
<font color="yellow">Dad, mother and I will make you
delicious dumplings later on.</font>

480
00:33:46,371 --> 00:33:49,038
<font color="yellow">So don't waste your energy looking for it.</font>

481
00:33:49,063 --> 00:33:50,852
<font color="yellow">I must find it.</font>

482
00:33:51,371 --> 00:33:54,058
<font color="yellow">I really want to pay them back
for the dumpling I ate.</font>

483
00:33:54,902 --> 00:33:57,832
<font color="yellow">One dumpling doesn't cost much.</font>

484
00:33:58,363 --> 00:34:00,933
<font color="yellow">One day, you'll be able to pay them back.</font>

485
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:03,573
<font color="yellow">Do you know how wide Seoul is?</font>

486
00:34:04,058 --> 00:34:06,051
<font color="yellow">You don't even know where it is. How will you</font>

487
00:34:06,076 --> 00:34:07,895
<font color="yellow">be able to find that small dumpling store?</font>

488
00:34:09,441 --> 00:34:12,410
<font color="yellow">But how did you know that
dumpling store is small?</font>

489
00:34:13,354 --> 00:34:16,149
<font color="yellow">Dumpling stores are usually small.</font>

490
00:34:16,691 --> 00:34:19,472
<font color="yellow">I've never seen big dumpling stores before.</font>

491
00:34:21,035 --> 00:34:25,399
<font color="yellow">Dad, later on, I'll go with you
to find the dumpling store.</font>

492
00:34:25,424 --> 00:34:27,649
<font color="yellow">- Really?
- Really.</font>

493
00:34:36,048 --> 00:34:38,023
<font color="yellow">- Enjoy.
- Thank you.</font>

494
00:34:40,931 --> 00:34:44,150
<font color="yellow">- It's freezing! I'm here, mother!
- Welcome!</font>

495
00:34:44,175 --> 00:34:45,353
<font color="yellow">I came to eat lunch.</font>

496
00:34:45,954 --> 00:34:47,154
<font color="yellow">Okay. Have a seat.</font>

497
00:34:47,179 --> 00:34:49,333
<font color="yellow">Where is Mi-poong? Why are you alone?</font>

498
00:34:49,790 --> 00:34:51,649
<font color="yellow">Oh, she went to make a delivery.</font>

499
00:34:51,923 --> 00:34:52,931
<font color="yellow">- Oh.
- Sit down.</font>

500
00:34:52,956 --> 00:34:54,469
<font color="yellow">- Okay.
- This place is delicious.</font>

501
00:34:54,494 --> 00:34:55,561
<font color="yellow">- It is?
- Yeah.</font>

502
00:34:55,595 --> 00:34:58,019
<font color="yellow">- Welcome!
- Welcome! Please sit here.</font>

503
00:35:00,837 --> 00:35:01,899
<font color="yellow">What would you like?</font>

504
00:35:01,924 --> 00:35:03,798
<font color="yellow">- Dumpling soup.
- Three dumpling soup.</font>

505
00:35:03,823 --> 00:35:05,024
<font color="yellow">- Three dumpling soup.
- Yes.</font>

506
00:35:05,049 --> 00:35:06,481
<font color="yellow">Three dumpling soup, mother!</font>

507
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:08,431
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

508
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:17,446
<font color="yellow">- I'm back!
- Hi.</font>

509
00:35:19,281 --> 00:35:20,281
<font color="yellow">Jang-go.</font>

510
00:35:22,094 --> 00:35:23,259
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

511
00:35:23,284 --> 00:35:25,673
<font color="yellow">What else would I be doing?
I'm helping your mother.</font>

512
00:35:34,079 --> 00:35:36,110
<font color="yellow">Gosh, I'm busy!</font>

513
00:35:36,790 --> 00:35:38,010
<font color="yellow">What did you need to tell me?</font>

514
00:35:38,181 --> 00:35:42,522
<font color="yellow">If you're going to tell me not to
come here again, don't even start.</font>

515
00:35:42,694 --> 00:35:43,694
<font color="yellow">I'm not going to listen.</font>

516
00:35:43,969 --> 00:35:45,470
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, what's wrong with you?</font>

517
00:35:46,056 --> 00:35:49,806
<font color="yellow">Didn't you hear what I said? I told you
to never come back here again!</font>

518
00:35:49,831 --> 00:35:51,727
<font color="yellow">I told you to not even start with that.</font>

519
00:35:52,392 --> 00:35:53,392
<font color="yellow">Jang-go.</font>

520
00:35:53,962 --> 00:35:57,301
<font color="yellow">Our consideration period is
almost over. If we just go to court</font>

521
00:35:57,326 --> 00:36:00,165
<font color="yellow">and report our divorce,
we'll be completely strangers then.</font>

522
00:36:00,806 --> 00:36:02,465
<font color="yellow">So why on earth are you doing this?</font>

523
00:36:04,025 --> 00:36:07,553
<font color="yellow">If you do this, not only does it get harder
for me, but it'll get harder for you, too.</font>

524
00:36:08,314 --> 00:36:11,306
<font color="yellow">So please get over me as soon as you can.</font>

525
00:36:11,658 --> 00:36:14,774
<font color="yellow">Forget about me and go your way! Please!</font>

526
00:36:15,563 --> 00:36:17,963
<font color="yellow">Kim Mi-poong, must I tell you again?</font>

527
00:36:20,103 --> 00:36:21,325
<font color="yellow">I can't live without you.</font>

528
00:36:21,931 --> 00:36:24,462
<font color="yellow">Even now, I want to leave home
and get back together with you.</font>

529
00:36:24,487 --> 00:36:25,487
<font color="yellow">Jang-go!</font>

530
00:36:25,658 --> 00:36:26,858
<font color="yellow">Should we do that?</font>

531
00:36:27,830 --> 00:36:31,306
<font color="yellow">You saw what your mother did here yesterday.</font>

532
00:36:32,493 --> 00:36:33,876
<font color="yellow">So how can you say that?</font>

533
00:36:35,462 --> 00:36:39,602
<font color="yellow">Let's believe that time will
solve our issues with her.</font>

534
00:36:40,712 --> 00:36:45,661
<font color="yellow">When she sees us living happily with
our adorable kids, she'll come to accept us.</font>

535
00:36:46,126 --> 00:36:47,259
<font color="yellow">And when is that?</font>

536
00:36:49,071 --> 00:36:50,734
<font color="yellow">I don't want to be hurt any longer.</font>

537
00:36:51,141 --> 00:36:52,141
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

538
00:36:52,697 --> 00:36:58,720
<font color="yellow">I don't care about getting hurt, but I don't
want to see my mother getting hurt again.</font>

539
00:37:00,470 --> 00:37:04,009
<font color="yellow">So move on and have a clean, fresh start.</font>

540
00:37:05,337 --> 00:37:09,157
<font color="yellow">If we get a divorce and you meet an
amazing woman who your mother will like,</font>

541
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:13,666
<font color="yellow">you'll be able to forget about me, a lowly
woman who works at a dumpling store.</font>

542
00:37:13,986 --> 00:37:16,073
<font color="yellow">Are you really going to talk that way?</font>

543
00:37:16,798 --> 00:37:17,798
<font color="yellow">See you at court.</font>

544
00:37:19,431 --> 00:37:21,142
<font color="yellow">I'm going to pay you back for this!</font>

545
00:37:25,876 --> 00:37:27,317
<font color="yellow">You don't even know my how I feel.</font>

