00:37:36,244 --> 00:37:37,484
<font color="yellow">Hi, Mr. Kim.</font>

547
00:37:38,126 --> 00:37:40,231
<font color="yellow">You came early today, too.</font>

548
00:37:41,336 --> 00:37:45,181
<font color="yellow">Yes, well, when I thought about
how bored you would be without me,</font>

549
00:37:46,001 --> 00:37:48,353
<font color="yellow">I sped over here from Bundang.</font>

550
00:37:49,330 --> 00:37:55,223
<font color="yellow">Don't ever do that again! What will
