551
00:38:01,626 --> 00:38:05,048
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim, here is the record of today's sales.</font>

552
00:38:05,073 --> 00:38:06,670
<font color="yellow">Oh, yes.</font>

553
00:38:06,696 --> 00:38:07,762
<font color="yellow">Yes, right here.</font>

554
00:38:13,126 --> 00:38:17,945
<font color="yellow">Nam-yi, is this a six or a zero?</font>

555
00:38:18,228 --> 00:38:19,228
<font color="yellow">Where?</font>

556
00:38:19,970 --> 00:38:20,970
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

