00:38:38,423 --> 00:38:41,888
<font color="yellow">Won-bin, aren't you hungry?</font>

559
00:38:42,611 --> 00:38:45,408
<font color="yellow">Go downstairs and eat some bread.</font>

560
00:38:45,962 --> 00:38:49,444
<font color="yellow">Call your friends over and eat as
