561
00:38:50,056 --> 00:38:52,176
<font color="yellow">It's fine. I already bought bread.</font>

562
00:38:57,501 --> 00:38:59,380
<font color="yellow">Won-bin...</font>

563
00:39:00,236 --> 00:39:02,976
<font color="yellow">there are customers
going in and out of here,</font>

564
00:39:03,001 --> 00:39:05,436
<font color="yellow">so it's pretty noisy.
