566
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:09,354
<font color="yellow">A quiet and safe study room.</font>

567
00:39:10,103 --> 00:39:13,704
<font color="yellow">How about you go over there and study?</font>

568
00:39:13,729 --> 00:39:17,908
<font color="yellow">No. I study much better here.
