00:41:27,236 --> 00:41:29,720
<font color="yellow">Are you okay now? Are you feeling better?</font>

594
00:41:30,658 --> 00:41:32,876
<font color="yellow">No, I'm still sick.</font>

595
00:41:33,619 --> 00:41:35,352
<font color="yellow">Do you know why I'm sick?</font>

596
00:41:35,892 --> 00:41:39,400
<font color="yellow">Of course. You told me earlier.
You said you were sick because</font>

597
00:41:39,425 --> 00:41:42,375
<font color="yellow">you had gotten upset
when I had suddenly disappeared.</font>

598
00:41:42,884 --> 00:41:43,884
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

599
00:41:44,447 --> 00:41:48,400
<font color="yellow">And I'm also sick because
you keep saying whimsical things.</font>

600
00:41:50,158 --> 00:41:51,673
<font color="yellow">Whimsical things? Like what?</font>

601
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:55,204
<font color="yellow">When did I tell you that we were
going to have a surprise party?</font>

602
00:41:56,173 --> 00:41:59,367
<font color="yellow">You did say that. That's what you said.</font>

603
00:42:00,126 --> 00:42:02,907
<font color="yellow">You told me to sneak out so we
can prepare father's surprise party.</font>

604
00:42:03,095 --> 00:42:05,176
<font color="yellow">See? You're lying right now, too.</font>

605
00:42:05,718 --> 00:42:09,038
<font color="yellow">No. You're just saying
nonsense because you're ill.</font>

606
00:42:09,391 --> 00:42:11,746
<font color="yellow">No! You really said that!</font>

607
00:42:12,447 --> 00:42:16,683
<font color="yellow">You just imagined eating
that dumpling. It's not real.</font>

608
00:42:17,297 --> 00:42:20,977
<font color="yellow">You imagined being kidnapped
and cleaning up cow dung.</font>

609
00:42:21,524 --> 00:42:24,205
<font color="yellow">Something is wrong with your head.
It's all just your imagination.</font>

610
00:42:25,009 --> 00:42:27,896
<font color="yellow">You're just making it up,
like a cartoon movie.</font>

611
00:42:28,415 --> 00:42:29,415
<font color="yellow">No!</font>

612
00:42:32,173 --> 00:42:33,889
<font color="yellow">No. It's real.</font>

613
00:42:34,970 --> 00:42:36,712
<font color="yellow">Listen to me carefully.</font>

614
00:42:38,033 --> 00:42:41,189
<font color="yellow">If you keep saying weird things
and making up stories,</font>

615
00:42:41,744 --> 00:42:44,397
<font color="yellow">I'm going to tell grandfather
to lock you up in the hospital!</font>

616
00:42:46,821 --> 00:42:49,188
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae, what's wrong?</font>

617
00:42:50,751 --> 00:42:52,302
<font color="yellow">You're my daughter.</font>

618
00:42:53,572 --> 00:42:56,813
<font color="yellow">How can you be like this to your father?</font>

619
00:42:58,844 --> 00:42:59,977
<font color="yellow">So disrespectful.</font>

620
00:43:00,306 --> 00:43:03,569
<font color="yellow">So stop giving me a hard time!</font>

621
00:43:03,967 --> 00:43:05,399
<font color="yellow">Stop saying strange things!</font>

622
00:43:06,126 --> 00:43:07,126
<font color="yellow">Got it?</font>

623
00:43:07,892 --> 00:43:09,274
<font color="yellow">Aren't you going to answer me?</font>

624
00:43:09,299 --> 00:43:11,587
<font color="yellow">I got it...</font>

625
00:43:12,830 --> 00:43:18,340
<font color="yellow">I dare you to tell grandfather
or anyone else I said this to you.</font>

626
00:43:19,017 --> 00:43:20,438
<font color="yellow">I'll get you then!</font>

627
00:43:21,611 --> 00:43:22,611
<font color="yellow">Got it?</font>

628
00:43:23,751 --> 00:43:24,976
<font color="yellow">Aren't you going to answer me?</font>

629
00:43:25,001 --> 00:43:27,032
<font color="yellow">I got it.</font>

630
00:43:29,017 --> 00:43:34,345
<font color="yellow">- What are you two talking about?
- Hee-dong!</font>

631
00:43:34,869 --> 00:43:37,431
<font color="yellow">Yes, father. What is it?</font>

632
00:43:38,673 --> 00:43:39,813
<font color="yellow">It's nothing.</font>

633
00:43:40,798 --> 00:43:43,265
<font color="yellow">I was scolding him to
not go outside by himself.</font>

634
00:43:44,822 --> 00:43:46,089
<font color="yellow">Go downstairs, dad.</font>

635
00:43:46,626 --> 00:43:48,977
<font color="yellow">Don't forget what I said. Got it?</font>

636
00:43:59,556 --> 00:44:00,556
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae,</font>

637
00:44:02,837 --> 00:44:04,271
<font color="yellow">did you get angry at your father?</font>

638
00:44:04,931 --> 00:44:05,931
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

639
00:44:06,775 --> 00:44:09,056
<font color="yellow">I'm so upset because of him.</font>

640
00:44:09,900 --> 00:44:12,851
<font color="yellow">He keeps saying strange and whimsical things!</font>

641
00:44:14,673 --> 00:44:16,446
<font color="yellow">I don't know what I should do about him.</font>

642
00:44:27,610 --> 00:44:31,063
<font color="yellow">"Frailty, thy name is woman!"</font>

643
00:44:32,986 --> 00:44:35,853
<font color="yellow">"To be or not to be! That is the question!"</font>

644
00:44:38,572 --> 00:44:43,245
<font color="yellow">"Do you think all of you are so smart?
The soldiers will cut your heads off!"</font>

645
00:44:48,556 --> 00:44:49,556
<font color="yellow">"Oh, my love."</font>

646
00:44:51,205 --> 00:44:53,621
<font color="yellow">"Oh, my love! Juliet!"</font>

647
00:44:58,275 --> 00:45:01,407
<font color="yellow">Song Joo-ri! Joo-ri!</font>

648
00:45:02,212 --> 00:45:03,212
<font color="yellow">Joo-ri!</font>

649
00:45:04,259 --> 00:45:05,259
<font color="yellow">Song Joo-ri!</font>

650
00:45:07,767 --> 00:45:09,548
<font color="yellow">Joo-ri, why are you running away?</font>

651
00:45:10,274 --> 00:45:15,400
<font color="yellow">I wasn't running away. I have to go
home quickly. I was just going my way.</font>

652
00:45:20,392 --> 00:45:22,485
<font color="yellow">But what are you doing here?</font>

653
00:45:26,072 --> 00:45:27,667
<font color="yellow">My friend lives around here.</font>

654
00:45:28,126 --> 00:45:31,048
<font color="yellow">I saw you coincidentally while I was
on my way home after meeting her.</font>

655
00:45:32,900 --> 00:45:35,233
<font color="yellow">But what's the point of meeting up?</font>

656
00:45:35,665 --> 00:45:37,329
<font color="yellow">We have nothing to say to each other.</font>

657
00:45:38,298 --> 00:45:41,077
<font color="yellow">That's why I was going
to just ignore you. Really.</font>

658
00:45:42,572 --> 00:45:44,298
<font color="yellow">What about the kids? Are they doing well?</font>

659
00:45:45,681 --> 00:45:47,399
<font color="yellow">Yes, they're doing well.</font>

660
00:45:50,206 --> 00:45:51,454
<font color="yellow">What about your husband?</font>

661
00:45:54,275 --> 00:45:56,832
<font color="yellow">He's doing well, of course.</font>

662
00:45:58,113 --> 00:46:00,980
<font color="yellow">What about you? Are you doing well, too?</font>

663
00:46:02,317 --> 00:46:06,918
<font color="yellow">Of course I am. There's no reason
I wouldn't be doing well.</font>

664
00:46:09,160 --> 00:46:10,160
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

665
00:46:10,652 --> 00:46:12,324
<font color="yellow">As long as you're doing well, it's fine.</font>

666
00:46:14,918 --> 00:46:15,918
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

667
00:46:16,863 --> 00:46:18,199
<font color="yellow">I'll be going now.</font>

668
00:46:18,645 --> 00:46:21,441
<font color="yellow">Jang-soo, I hope you'll be happy, too.</font>

669
00:46:58,715 --> 00:46:59,941
<font color="yellow">Hi. It's me, Jang-soo.</font>

670
00:47:00,598 --> 00:47:03,005
<font color="yellow">You said you know Joo-ri's friend, right?</font>

671
00:47:04,473 --> 00:47:06,333
<font color="yellow">Find out how Joo-ri is doing lately.</font>

672
00:47:08,363 --> 00:47:10,285
<font color="yellow">Yes. Help me out.</font>

673
00:47:16,262 --> 00:47:17,277
<font color="yellow">Did you just come home?</font>

674
00:47:17,302 --> 00:47:19,928
<font color="yellow">Yes. I had plans with my friends.
It's been a while</font>

675
00:47:19,953 --> 00:47:22,325
<font color="yellow">since I met them,
so I went shopping with them.</font>

676
00:47:23,543 --> 00:47:24,933
<font color="yellow">I don't think it's been a while.</font>

677
00:47:25,457 --> 00:47:28,863
<font color="yellow">You've been coming home late these days
because you're hanging out with your friends.</font>

678
00:47:28,888 --> 00:47:29,888
<font color="yellow">I have?</font>

679
00:47:30,177 --> 00:47:32,668
<font color="yellow">Some days I'm late. Some days I'm not.</font>

680
00:47:34,082 --> 00:47:38,893
<font color="yellow">Now that Mi-poong isn't around, can you
come home earlier and help out my mom a bit?</font>

681
00:47:39,551 --> 00:47:42,550
<font color="yellow">Jang-soo, do you think
I've been playing around all this time?</font>

682
00:47:44,434 --> 00:47:46,770
<font color="yellow">I've been working all day long.
It's been a while</font>

683
00:47:46,795 --> 00:47:49,144
<font color="yellow">since I saw my friends, so I ate
dinner and had coffee with them.</font>

684
00:47:49,169 --> 00:47:50,836
<font color="yellow">Are you that unhappy with it?</font>

685
00:47:51,121 --> 00:47:52,707
<font color="yellow">I'm not saying I'm unhappy with it.</font>

686
00:47:53,902 --> 00:47:56,574
<font color="yellow">I just feel bad for my mom because
you're always late these days.</font>

687
00:47:56,722 --> 00:48:00,215
<font color="yellow">If you feel that bad for her,
you can help her out then!</font>

688
00:48:00,590 --> 00:48:02,981
<font color="yellow">I'm going to wash up,
so go ahead and sleep first!</font>

689
00:48:16,613 --> 00:48:18,043
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

690
00:48:19,793 --> 00:48:21,308
<font color="yellow">You can't sleep?</font>

691
00:48:27,683 --> 00:48:28,699
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

692
00:48:31,231 --> 00:48:33,223
<font color="yellow">I'm really curious about something.</font>

693
00:48:35,254 --> 00:48:36,483
<font color="yellow">Curious?</font>

694
00:48:37,692 --> 00:48:38,996
<font color="yellow">About what?</font>

695
00:48:41,129 --> 00:48:42,707
<font color="yellow">About Shin-ae...</font>

696
00:48:45,621 --> 00:48:47,354
<font color="yellow">Is she really my daughter?</font>

697
00:48:50,863 --> 00:48:53,496
<font color="yellow">Yes, she's really your daughter.</font>

698
00:48:54,605 --> 00:48:56,373
<font color="yellow">Were you worried about that?</font>

699
00:48:58,254 --> 00:48:59,254
<font color="yellow">But father...</font>

700
00:49:01,215 --> 00:49:03,748
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae doesn't feel like my daughter.</font>

701
00:49:04,074 --> 00:49:05,434
<font color="yellow">Do you still feel that way?</font>

702
00:49:06,800 --> 00:49:12,062
<font color="yellow">I think that's because your memory
hasn't returned yet.</font>

703
00:49:12,449 --> 00:49:15,287
<font color="yellow">I don't that's it, father.</font>

704
00:49:17,668 --> 00:49:21,948
<font color="yellow">When I'm with you,
I feel comfortable and happy.</font>

705
00:49:23,481 --> 00:49:26,839
<font color="yellow">I'm scared of Shin-ae though.</font>

706
00:49:28,223 --> 00:49:31,168
<font color="yellow">You're scared of Shin-ae?</font>

707
00:49:31,481 --> 00:49:35,027
<font color="yellow">She keeps saying that I'm lying.</font>

708
00:49:36,824 --> 00:49:41,707
<font color="yellow">- She keeps getting mad at me, too.
- Shin-ae got mad at you?</font>

709
00:49:42,902 --> 00:49:47,310
<font color="yellow">She said she'll get me if I told you this.</font>

710
00:49:48,840 --> 00:49:53,636
<font color="yellow">She said she would send me
to the hospital, father.</font>

711
00:49:54,715 --> 00:49:58,088
<font color="yellow">That's why I'm really scared of her, father.</font>

712
00:49:59,238 --> 00:50:02,191
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae really said that?</font>

713
00:50:03,683 --> 00:50:04,935
<font color="yellow">Yes, she really did.</font>

714
00:50:06,840 --> 00:50:11,169
<font color="yellow">So I'm really scared of her father.</font>

715
00:51:05,085 --> 00:51:07,898
<font color="yellow">What's going on? Did Mr. Kim
just go up to see Dal-ho?</font>

716
00:51:08,523 --> 00:51:10,265
<font color="yellow">Why now?</font>

717
00:51:13,531 --> 00:51:17,077
<font color="yellow">Why is he going up at this hour?
What's going on?</font>

718
00:51:22,281 --> 00:51:23,881
<font color="yellow">What brings you up here?</font>

719
00:51:25,836 --> 00:51:26,836
<font color="yellow">Dal-ho.</font>

720
00:51:27,601 --> 00:51:28,601
<font color="yellow">Yes, Mr. Kim.</font>

721
00:51:29,817 --> 00:51:32,707
<font color="yellow">About Shin-ae...</font>

722
00:51:33,685 --> 00:51:38,634
<font color="yellow">Last time, I couldn't check on her because
doing a DNA test with her was impossible,</font>

723
00:51:40,482 --> 00:51:46,036
<font color="yellow">but wouldn't it be possible for Shin-ae
and Dae-hoon to get a DNA test now?</font>

724
00:51:47,044 --> 00:51:49,526
<font color="yellow">Yes, of course. Fathers
and daughters can be tested.</font>

725
00:51:50,193 --> 00:51:51,193
<font color="yellow">Then Dal-ho...</font>

726
00:51:52,864 --> 00:51:57,072
<font color="yellow">I think Shin-ae and Dae-hoon
should get a DNA test.</font>

727
00:51:58,872 --> 00:52:00,329
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

728
00:52:01,122 --> 00:52:06,802
<font color="yellow">So I wanted to run the test
without Shin-ae knowing about it.</font>

729
00:52:07,368 --> 00:52:09,101
<font color="yellow">That's why I came up here.</font>

730
00:52:09,611 --> 00:52:12,194
<font color="yellow">You're the only one
who I can discuss this with.</font>

731
00:52:14,040 --> 00:52:15,440
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, Mr. Kim.</font>

732
00:52:15,898 --> 00:52:18,973
<font color="yellow">When Shin-ae goes to work tomorrow,
I'll get her toothbrush</font>

733
00:52:18,998 --> 00:52:21,867
<font color="yellow">and Dae-hoon's toothbrush
and take them for DNA testing.</font>

734
00:52:22,906 --> 00:52:25,829
<font color="yellow">Yes, Dal-ho. Please help me out.</font>

735
00:52:27,328 --> 00:52:28,328
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

736
00:52:30,109 --> 00:52:31,507
<font color="yellow">DNA test?</font>

737
00:52:34,383 --> 00:52:36,885
<font color="yellow">Oh, no! What kind of bolt out
of the blue is this?</font>

738
00:53:05,367 --> 00:53:09,619
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae, we're in big trouble! It's an
emergency! Come to my room at once!</font>

739
00:53:10,453 --> 00:53:13,616
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim is with Dal-ho right now,
so be careful when you come down!</font>

740
00:53:14,617 --> 00:53:18,273
<font color="yellow">Are you sleeping?
This isn't the time to sleep!</font>

741
00:53:34,336 --> 00:53:36,399
<font color="yellow">Mother, what's going on?</font>

742
00:53:36,789 --> 00:53:38,848
<font color="yellow">Shin-ae, what do we do? We're in big trouble!</font>

743
00:53:39,866 --> 00:53:44,874
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim is going to run a DNA test
on you and his son tomorrow.</font>

744
00:53:45,202 --> 00:53:47,070
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

745
00:53:47,546 --> 00:53:49,187
<font color="yellow">DNA test?</font>

746
00:53:57,508 --> 00:54:01,352
<font color="yellow">(Father's Dumplings)</font>

747
00:54:09,531 --> 00:54:12,585
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear. How could I forget?</font>

748
00:54:13,078 --> 00:54:14,078
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

749
00:54:14,103 --> 00:54:18,141
<font color="yellow">I made kimchi dumplings last night
and left them in the refrigerator.</font>

750
00:54:18,166 --> 00:54:20,819
<font color="yellow">Oh, mom. I'll go home and get them.</font>

751
00:54:20,844 --> 00:54:23,019
<font color="yellow">No, I'll go.</font>

752
00:54:26,969 --> 00:54:28,502
<font color="yellow">- I'll be back.
- Okay.</font>

753
00:54:38,289 --> 00:54:39,967
<font color="yellow">- Hi.
- Hello!</font>

754
00:54:39,992 --> 00:54:42,942
<font color="yellow">- Please give me two packs of dumplings.
- Sure. Wait just a moment.</font>

755
00:54:43,711 --> 00:54:46,168
<font color="yellow">The customers at my hair salon
kept saying how delicious</font>

756
00:54:46,193 --> 00:54:48,391
<font color="yellow">your dumplings are,
so I came to taste them myself.</font>

757
00:54:48,416 --> 00:54:51,796
<font color="yellow">Oh, really? Come often.
They're very delicious.</font>

758
00:54:54,039 --> 00:54:55,039
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

759
00:54:55,320 --> 00:54:58,587
<font color="yellow">Oh, it's a flier searching
for my missing father.</font>

760
00:54:58,984 --> 00:55:01,401
<font color="yellow">I thought he died while
we were escaping North Korea,</font>

761
00:55:01,426 --> 00:55:03,663
<font color="yellow">but I think he's alive,
so I'm trying to find him.</font>

762
00:55:04,209 --> 00:55:05,209
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

763
00:55:05,359 --> 00:55:08,998
<font color="yellow">Then I'll take a few of these
and post them up in my hair salon.</font>

764
00:55:09,023 --> 00:55:12,093
<font color="yellow">Really? Thank you so much!</font>

765
00:55:13,320 --> 00:55:17,011
<font color="yellow">- You can just take these today.
I won't take your money.
- Are you sure?</font>

766
00:55:17,036 --> 00:55:21,356
<font color="yellow">Yes. You're putting up my fliers in your salon,
so how could I accept your money?</font>

767
00:55:21,457 --> 00:55:24,163
<font color="yellow">Then I'll come by tomorrow
for lunch and try your dumpling soup.</font>

768
00:55:25,015 --> 00:55:27,311
<font color="yellow">- Okay. Bye!
- Bye.</font>

769
00:55:27,336 --> 00:55:29,273
<font color="yellow">Enjoy!</font>

770
00:55:33,906 --> 00:55:36,179
<font color="yellow">Hurry up and open it, mister!</font>

771
00:55:37,085 --> 00:55:40,799
<font color="yellow">You're awfully impatient. Please be still.
I'm trying my best to open it right now.</font>

772
00:55:41,398 --> 00:55:43,985
<font color="yellow">Are you sure you can open doors?
Why are you so slow?</font>

773
00:55:44,773 --> 00:55:46,468
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, are you sure this is your house?</font>

774
00:55:47,547 --> 00:55:50,662
<font color="yellow">Of course I am! I'm just cold, so hurry up!</font>

775
00:55:53,633 --> 00:55:54,633
<font color="yellow">It's done.</font>

776
00:55:54,658 --> 00:55:56,398
<font color="yellow">Here. Hurry up and go.</font>

777
00:55:57,030 --> 00:55:58,030
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

778
00:56:04,453 --> 00:56:05,598
<font color="yellow">Where's the bathroom?</font>

779
00:56:07,594 --> 00:56:08,594
<font color="yellow">Is it here?</font>

780
00:56:30,414 --> 00:56:32,466
<font color="yellow">Oh, that's strange. I know I had definitely</font>

781
00:56:32,491 --> 00:56:34,635
<font color="yellow">locked the door before I left. Why is it open?</font>

782
00:56:50,258 --> 00:56:54,296
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

783
00:56:55,242 --> 00:56:59,160
<font color="yellow">What are you doing inside
my house with your shoes on?</font>

784
00:56:59,371 --> 00:57:00,562
<font color="yellow">Are you a thief?</font>

785
00:57:00,844 --> 00:57:02,487
<font color="yellow">What? A thief?</font>

786
00:57:02,992 --> 00:57:04,589
<font color="yellow">How dare you call me a thief!</font>

787
00:57:05,492 --> 00:57:08,716
<font color="yellow">You're the thief! A husband-stealing thief!</font>

788
00:57:09,250 --> 00:57:10,383
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

789
00:57:11,789 --> 00:57:17,019
<font color="yellow">Is that why came into
